ActPilotage Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Atlantic Pilotage Tariff Regulations, 1996
PrecisRegulations amending the ATLANTIC PILOTAGE TARIFF REGULATIONS, 1996 in order to enable the Authority to meet its mandate to operate a safe and efficient pilotage service within the Atlantic region, while achieving financial self-sufficiency of individual ports (i.e. avoiding cross-subsidization).
